des:
Fixes:
• Fixed the incredibly small chance of the automsg locking up if the run time was exactly 25,000 milliseconds (yes, it actually happened)
• Thumbcache error should be patched
• Updated support server link

This version re-adds the Aternos patch.

Changes:
• Completely revamped the botstats command with more information
• Bot will now show the last reachable date for an offline server in the automsg as a relative time instead of a datestamp

Fixes:
• Re-added the patch for Aternos and Minefort reporting as online when the server is stopped. This was accidentally looked over after the 2.1 rewrite.
